										</ol>
									</statement>
								</investigation>
					
					
								
								<activity>
									<statement>
										<p>
											Consider the election run in <xref ref="act-irv1" />.
											Suppose that the three voters in the rightmost column of <xref ref="table-irv" /> change their preferences to <m>A \succ D \succ C \succ B</m>.
											Note that this change is favorable only to candidate <m>A</m>.
										</p>
										<ol>
