											<li>Compare your answer to Question 1 of this activity to Question 3 of <xref ref="act-irv1" />. What conclusions can you draw?</li>
											<li>Do some research on <url href="https://www.fairvote.org">FairVote.org</url> about this phenomenon. How do they respond to a potential critique?</li>
										</ol>
									</statement>
								</activity>
								
								<investigation>
									<statement>
										<p>Consider an election between three candidates with the preference schedule shown in <xref ref="table-irv3" />.</p>
										
